Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.83,0:00:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.46,0:00:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的景色真不錯 悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.42,0:00:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託不要在我頭上吃甜瓜麵包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麵包屑撒得到處都是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃了不就行了 你吃了不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.92,0:00:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等會清理很麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候被罵是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 葉卡特琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是想和悠二一起看這裡的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不殺不足以消老娘之恨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣竹竿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:51.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明一點也不瞭解悠二
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我現在要開始瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.62,0:00:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:00:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能就是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.95,0:00:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.98,0:00:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:03.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個噁心的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,釘（消聲）理惠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神啊 惡魔啊 聽我的呼喚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.74,0:01:09.31,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：源自拉丁語咒語Eloim,Essaim,frugativi et appelavi 山田風太郎的小說「魔界轉生」改編的電影中天草四郎時貞的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤田研二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.64,0:01:10.56,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：「魔界轉生」1981年電影版天草四郎時貞的扮演者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.21,0:01:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烤肉套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.49,0:01:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起烤肉來 還是生薑燒肉更好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.72,0:01:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬肉菜餚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.11,0:01:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.94,0:01:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.85,0:01:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:02.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是吉田一美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛 這樣直勾勾地看著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二 不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.46,0:02:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田一美的胸不是大得過分了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一般啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.39,0:02:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在引誘我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.74,0:02:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠二你是笨蛋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.83,0:02:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉卡特琳娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嘿 衝啊 衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.18,0:02:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我燒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葉卡特琳娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在燃燒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.63,0:02:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(710,0)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord4}次日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嘿 前進 前進
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 你的狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.70,0:03:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的狗換了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(710,0)}{\1c&H000000&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&}{\bord4}再次日
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀嘿 衝啊 衝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 坂井同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我燒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的狗也換得太勤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 什麼嘛 什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是流行女僕我不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過沒必要這麼做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.83,0:04:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齷鹺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.87,0:04:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.11,0:04:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種再說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.30,0:04:17.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 誰齷鹺了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,齷鹺 醜陋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 你果然是我齷鹺的搭檔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣竹竿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.23,0:04:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 第二次競爭 Start
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好好加油吧 小不點夏娜 嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:59.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小還滿有幹勁的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不小 才不小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.89,0:05:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個噁心的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,川（消聲）綾子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾身為鐵 心已空 天魔覆滅是也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:15.41,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：原句為：我が身すでに鐵なり我が心すでに空なり天魔覆滅！ 出自連續劇「影之軍團」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千葉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.70,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,註：千葉真一 「影之軍團」中服部半藏的扮演者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.13,0:05:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.16,0:05:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生薑燒肉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.21,0:05:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:24.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豬肉菜餚  這是之前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次 從危機中逃了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來又遇到新的難題了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.92,0:05:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這裡…究竟是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.28,0:05:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體感溫度下降了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.78,0:05:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 風聲讓人毛骨悚然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.61,0:05:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 通過了狹長隧道之後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.24,0:05:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來到眼前一片白色的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.38,0:06:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點夏娜 回來了



